CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 7, 1961, pg. A31 reads: "Winners All - Winners and runners-up in annual Dandy Duffer Club tournament are shown with their trophies, which were presented at the club's Awards Night, recently, at the Vogue Terrace. Left to right, back row: Louis Johnson, James Wise, John Trent, James Chapman Jr., Dave Goodman, Warren Breyard, Andrew Dent, Joseph Preston and Harvey Gravely.  Seated: Jack Ethridge, Wilbur (Mickey) Lewis, Jack Grover, club champion; Charles Hinton and James Dyer.  Kneeling, forefront, is tournament director William Browne, who made the presentations. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Dandy Duffer Club winners, from left, Dave Goodman, Jack Grover, unknown man, William Browne, Wilbur (Mickey) Lewis, and Charles Hinton, posed with trophies in Vogue Terrace, East McKeesport
